{"lemma":"خَلَفَ","slug":"خَلَفَ","root":"خ.ل.ف","root_slug":"خ-ل-ف","root_link":"/words/roots/خ-ل-ف","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"خَلَفَ","root":"خلف","pos":"V","occurrence_count":5},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":4,"pos_tags":["noun","prep","verb"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":20},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n11341"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AE%D9%8E%D9%84%D9%8E%D9%81%D9%8E"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"prep","gloss":"behind","examples":[{"text":"بَدَأَت جُو تَمْشِي ذَهَابًا وَإِيَابًا وَيَدَاهَا خَلْفَ ظَهْرِهَا، كَٱلرَّجُلِ.","english":"Joe started walking back and forth with her hands behind her back, like a man."}]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of خَلَفَ (ḵalafa) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"location that is behind"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"time past"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"back"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"successor, descendant"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"descendants"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"remnant of people"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"succeeding generation, progeny"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"short rib"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"someone absent from the tribe or just returned"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to succeed, to follow, to come after"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to substitute for"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to replace"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to lag behind"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to stay behind"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to be detained, to stay away"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to appoint as a successor"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to leave behind"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to have offspring","tags":["intransitive"]}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"From Proto-Semitic *ḫalap-. Cognate with Biblical Hebrew חָלַף (ḥɔlap̄, “to move past”)."},"ipa":["/xal.fa/","/xalf/","/xa.la.fa/","/xal.la.fa/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n11341","headword_ar":"خَلَفَ","root":"xlf","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xalofN","text_ar":"خَلْفٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He came after, followed, succeeded,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"remained after, another,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"another that had perished"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"died."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) Hence, in the Kur [vii. 168 and xix. 60],"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faxalafa","text_ar":"فَخَلَفَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mino baEodihimo xalofN","text_ar":"مِنْ بَعْدِهِمْ خَلْفٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"And there hath succeeded them,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"come after them,"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a posterity,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an evil posterity."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Bd in xix. 60.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xalafahu","text_ar":"خَلَفَهُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He came after him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dbr","text_ar":"دبر"},{"kind":"text","text":", Mgh, Msb, TA,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"behind him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A ubi suprà, Mgh,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"following him nearly;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A ubi suprà;) inf. n. as above, (Mgh, TA,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xilofapN","text_ar":"خِلْفَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"also: (Mgh:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he remained after him:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaA='a xilaAfahu","text_ar":"جَا=ءَ خِلَافَهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"likewise signifies [the same as"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jA=' xalofahu","text_ar":"جا=ء خَلْفَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; an inf. n. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaAlafa","text_ar":"خَالَفَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"being thus used as an adv. n.; i. e.]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he came after him."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) You say also,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xalafa All~ayolu","text_ar":"خَلَفَ اللَّيْلُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aln~ahaAra","text_ar":"النَّهَارَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xalofN","text_ar":"خَلْفٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xilofapN","text_ar":"خِلْفَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The night followed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"came after, the day."},{"kind":"text","text":"(MA.) ―         -b2-  [Hence,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xalafotuhu","text_ar":"خَلَفْتُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", [aor. as above,] inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xalofN","text_ar":"خَلْفٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", [perhaps a mistranscription for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xalafa","text_ar":"خَلَفَ"},{"kind":"text","text":",]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I was, after him, a substitute for him:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I supplied his place:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I superseded him."},{"kind":"text","text":"] And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xalafahu","text_ar":"خَلَفَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (aor. as above, TA,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xilaAfapN","text_ar":"خِلَافَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Mgh, Msb, K, TA) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xalafN","text_ar":"خَلَفٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xil~iyqaY","text_ar":"خِلِّيقَى"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, * K, * TA,) which last is an inf. n. of the intensive kind, (Sgh, MF, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, his"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaliyfap","text_ar":"خَلِيفَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"successor,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"vice-agent,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.], (S, Mgh, Msb, K,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"his substitute;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA;)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiY qawomihi","text_ar":"فِى قَوْمِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"among,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in respect of, his people"},{"kind":"text","text":"], (S, TA,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aholihi","text_ar":"اَهْلِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"his family"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; relating to good and to evil; wherefore one says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^awoSaY lahu biAlxilaAfapi","text_ar":"اَوْصَى لَهُ بِالخِلَافَةِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he charged him by his will with the being his successor,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"vice-agent,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.]; (TA;) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EalaY A^aholihi wamaAlihi","text_ar":"عَلَى اَهْلِهِ وَمَالِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"over his family and his property"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (Msb:) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Axtflhu","text_ar":"اختفلهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies the same; (Lh, Ibn-'Abbád, K;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, his"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaliyfap","text_ar":"خَلِيفَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Ibn-'Abbád, TA)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"after him."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Ibn-'Abbád, TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xalafa fulaAnFA","text_ar":"خَلَفَ فُلَانًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"[alone]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaliyfapN","text_ar":"خَلِيفَةٌ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of such a one among,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in respect of, his family"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and his children."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xalafahu rab~uhu fiY A^aholihi","text_ar":"خَلَفَهُ رَبُّهُ فِى اَهْلِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waladihi","text_ar":"وَلَدِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xilaAfapN","text_ar":"خِلَافَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"His Lord was [for him] a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaliyfap","text_ar":"خَلِيفَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"supplier of his place] to his family"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"his children."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA. [In the CK,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Axlf","text_ar":"اخلف"},{"kind":"text","text":"is made to signify the same; but this is in consequence of an omission.]) And one says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xalafa A@ll~`hu Ealayoka","text_ar":"خَلَفَ ا@للّٰهُ عَلَيْكَ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"May God be to to thee a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaliyfap","text_ar":"خَلِيفَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"supplier of the place"},{"kind":"text","text":"] (S, Msb, K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of thy father;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the one whom thou hast lost:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb, K:) thus one says to one who has lost by death his father (S, Msb, K) or mother (K) or paternal uncle (S, Msb) or any other who cannot be replaced: (Msb, K:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xalafa A@ll~`hu","text_ar":"خَلَفَ ا@للّٰهُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ealayoka xayorFA","text_ar":"عَلَيْكَ خَيْرًا"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bixayorK","text_ar":"بِخَيْرٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (AZ, Msb, K,) or both, (L,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xalafa A@ll~`hu laka bixayorK","text_ar":"خَلَفَ ا@للّٰهُ لَكَ بِخَيْرٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (AZ, Msb,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A@ll~`hu Ealayoka xayorFA","text_ar":"ا@للّٰهُ عَلَيْكَ خَيْرًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^axolafa","text_ar":"اَخْلَفَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laka xayorFA","text_ar":"لَكَ خَيْرًا"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K: [in which it is implied that these phrases mean"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"May God supply to thee well the place of him whom thou hast lost:"},{"kind":"text","text":"but it is implied in the Msb that the two of them there mentioned mean"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"May God restore to thee good in the place of that which has gone from thee:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and it appears from what here follows that all of these phrases have the latter meaning, whether or not they have the former meaning also:]) to him who has lost property or a child or a thing [of any other kind] of which the replacement may be asked, (S,) or to him of whom that which may be replaced has perished, or died, (K,) one says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A@ll~`hu Ealayoka","text_ar":"ا@للّٰهُ عَلَيْكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^axolafa","text_ar":"اَخْلَفَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb, K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"May God restore to thee the like of that which has gone from thee,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"may God restore to thee what has gone from thee;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K in a later part of the art.;) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"All~`h laka","text_ar":"اللّٰه لَكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Axlf","text_ar":"اخلف","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xalafa All~`h lk","text_ar":"خَلَفَ اللّٰه لك"},{"kind":"text","text":": or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xalafa All~`h Ealayoka","text_ar":"خَلَفَ اللّٰه عَلَيْكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is allowable in relation to property and the like; and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yaxolafu","text_ar":"يَخْلَفُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yamonaEu","text_ar":"يَمْنَعُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is allowable as its aor., though extr., (K,) as it has no faucial letter to occasion the fet-h: (TA:) and one says also,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xalafa A@ll~`hu laka","text_ar":"خَلَفَ ا@للّٰهُ لَكَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bixayorK","text_ar":"بِخَيْرٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"May God give thee good in the place of that which has gone from thee;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA;) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ealayoka xayorFA","text_ar":"عَلَيْكَ خَيْرًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Axlf","text_ar":"اخلف","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb, TA,) meaning the same; (TA;) and [so]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laka xayorFA","text_ar":"لَكَ خَيْرًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Axlf","text_ar":"اخلف","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bixayorK","text_ar":"بِخَيْرٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":": and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A@ll~`hu Ealayoka maAlaka","text_ar":"ا@للّٰهُ عَلَيْكَ مَالَكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Axlf","text_ar":"اخلف","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laka maAlaka","text_ar":"لَكَ مَالَكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"May God restore,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"replace, to thee thy property"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (Msb.)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xalafa A^abaAhu","text_ar":"خَلَفَ اَبَاهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA,) means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He became behind his father;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K;) and if so, its inf. n. is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xalofN","text_ar":"خَلْفٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA:) or it means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he became in the place of his father;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K;) and if so, its inf. n. is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xalafN","text_ar":"خَلَفٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xalafa makaAna A^abiyhi","text_ar":"خَلَفَ مَكَانَ اَبِيهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xilaAfapN","text_ar":"خِلَافَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xalafN","text_ar":"خَلَفٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he became in the place of his father, exclusively of every other."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.) You say also,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xalafati AlfaAkihapi baEoDuhaA baEoDFA","text_ar":"خَلَفَتِ الفَاكِهَةِ بَعْضُهَا بَعْضًا"},{"kind":"text","text":", (JK, K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xalofN","text_ar":"خَلْفٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (JK, TA,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xalafN","text_ar":"خَلَفٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA, [the former being there altered to the latter (which is the more probably correct), or the latter to the former,]) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xilofapN","text_ar":"خِلْفَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (JK, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The fruit replaced other fruit;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became substituted for other fruit."},{"kind":"text","text":"(JK, * K,* TA. [In the CK,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SaAra xalofFA","text_ar":"صَارَ خَلْفًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"is erroneously put for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SaArato xalafFA","text_ar":"صَارَتْ خَلَفًا"},{"kind":"text","text":".]) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xalafa fulaAnN","text_ar":"خَلَفَ فُلَانٌ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EalaY fulaAnapa","text_ar":"عَلَى فُلَانَةَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xilaAfapN","text_ar":"خِلَافَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", [like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eaqaba EalayohaA","text_ar":"عَقَبَ عَلَيْهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":",]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Such a man took as his wife such a woman after another husband [and thus supplied his place]."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Z, TA.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xalafa ulaAnFA","text_ar":"خَلَفَ ُلَانًا"},{"kind":"text","text":", (aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He took,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"seized, such a one from behind him;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(JK, * K;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Axtlfhu","text_ar":"اختلفهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) And hence, (TA,)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xalafa lahu","text_ar":"خَلَفَ لَهُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"biAls~ayofi","text_ar":"بِالسَّيْفِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(JK, TA)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He came to him from behind him, and smote his neck,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"struck off his head, with the sword."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xalafa fulaAnN biEaqibiY","text_ar":"خَلَفَ فُلَانٌ بِعَقِبِى"},{"kind":"text","text":"[is explained as meaning]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Such a one stayed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"abode, after me."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eqb","text_ar":"عقب"},{"kind":"text","text":") [But] ―         -b5-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xalafa","text_ar":"خَلَفَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"biEaqabi fulaAnK","text_ar":"بِعَقَبِ فُلَانٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is said by some to mean"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_ilaY","text_ar":"اـِلَى"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaAlafahu","text_ar":"خَالَفَهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aholihi","text_ar":"اَهْلِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[q. v.]: accord. to As, however, it means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He parted with such a one on the condition of doing a certain thing, and then came behind him"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"behind his back"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and did another thing after parting with him:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and Az says that this is a more correct explanation than the former one. (TA.) [Hence, app.,] one says also,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_in~a A@moraA^apa fulaAnK","text_ar":"اـِنَّ ا@مْرَاَةَ فُلَانٍ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taxolufu zawojahaA biAln~izaAEi A_ilaY gayorihi A_i*aA gaAba EanohaA","text_ar":"تَخْلُفُ زَوْجَهَا بِالنِّزَاعِ اـِلَى غَيْرِهِ اـِذَا غَابَ عَنْهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Verily the wife of such a one is unfaithful to her husband by yearning towards another when he is absent from her:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"deceives her husband behind his back by yearning towards another;"},{"kind":"text","text":"for it is implied, by an ex. given, that"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A*A gAb EnhA","text_ar":"اذا غاب عنها"},{"kind":"text","text":"is added by way of explanation]. (TA.)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xalafahu","text_ar":"خَلَفَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"also signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He spoke of him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"mentioned him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"behind his back,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"when he was not present:"},{"kind":"text","text":"so in the phrase,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xalafahu bixayorK","text_ar":"خَلَفَهُ بِخَيْرٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bi$ar~K","text_ar":"بِشَرٍّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He spoke of him behind his back well"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ill"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) And one says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yaxolufu Aln~aAsa mino waraAy^ihimo","text_ar":"يَخْلُفُ النَّاسَ مِنْ وَرَايِهِمْ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He defames men behind their backs"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: the action signified hereby is like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"giybapN","text_ar":"غِيبَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and may be ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"by making signs"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with the side of the mouth,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with the eye,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with the head."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"hmz","text_ar":"همز"},{"kind":"text","text":".) ―         -b6-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xalafa Eano A^aSoHaAbihi","text_ar":"خَلَفَ عَنْ اَصْحَابِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K, TA,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He remained behind,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"after, his companions; did not go forth with them;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aSoHaAbihi","text_ar":"اَصْحَابِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaEada xilaAfa","text_ar":"قَعَدَ خِلَافَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"[similar to a phrase mentioned near the beginning of this"},{"kind":"page_break","n":793},{"kind":"text","text":"art.]; (TA;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"txl~f","text_ar":"تخلّف","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (K in explanation of the former phrase;) which is syn. with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taA^ax~ara","text_ar":"تَاَخَّرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, K;) as in the phrase"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"txl~f Ean~iY","text_ar":"تخلّف عَنِّى"},{"kind":"text","text":"[which means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He remained behind me,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"after me"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; (S;) [for]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"txl~f Eanohu","text_ar":"تخلّف عَنْهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"means"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baqiYa xalofahu","text_ar":"بَقِىَ خَلْفَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (Mgh;) and [in like manner] you say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"txl~f Eani lAqawomi","text_ar":"تخلّف عَنِ لاقَوْمِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He remained behind,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"after, the people,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"party, not going with them;"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he held back,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hung back, from them;"},{"kind":"text","text":"] and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaEadotu xilaAfahu","text_ar":"قَعَدْتُ خِلَافَهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I remained"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"behind him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"after him;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb;) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xAlf","text_ar":"خالف","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ean~aA","text_ar":"عَنَّا"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He remained behind us,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"after us;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn. ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"txl~f","text_ar":"تخلّف","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA, from a trad.) It is said in the Kur [xvii. 78],"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_il~aA qaliylFA","text_ar":"اـِلَّا قَلِيلًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wa A_i*aA laA yalobavuwna xilaAfaka","text_ar":"وَ اـِذَا لَا يَلْبَثُونَ خِلَافَكَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", i. e. ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"But in that case they should not have remained"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"after thee"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"save a little while"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (JK, TA: *) so accord. to one reading [instead of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xalofaka","text_ar":"خَلْفَكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", which means the same]. (TA.) And in like manner,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rasuwli A@ll~`hi","text_ar":"رَسُولِ ا@للّٰهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fariHa Almuxal~afuwna bimaqoEadihimo xilaAfa","text_ar":"فَرِحَ المُخَلَّفُونَ بِمَقْعَدِهِمْ خِلَافَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", in the Kur [ix. 82], means ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Those who were left behind rejoiced in their remaining"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"behind the Apostle of God:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, TA:) or the meaning here is,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muxaAlafapa rswl All~`h","text_ar":"مُخَالَفَةَ رسول اللّٰه"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in disagreement with the Apostle of God"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (JK, S:) thus says Lh; but IB disagrees with him; saying that"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xlAf","text_ar":"خلاف"},{"kind":"text","text":"here means"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baEoda","text_ar":"بَعْدَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and cites six exs. in which it has this meaning, from poets. (TA.) ―         -b7-  [Hence,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xalafa fulaAnN Eano kul~i xayorK","text_ar":"خَلَفَ فُلَانٌ عَنْ كُلِّ خَيْرٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Such a one was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, kept back from all good; i. e.,"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"did not prosper,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"was not successful."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA. [It is there added, that it is explained in the A as tropical, and as meaning"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tagay~ara wafasada","text_ar":"تَغَيَّرَ وَفَسَدَ"},{"kind":"text","text":": but this is perhaps a mistake, occasioned by the accidental omission of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waxalafa All~abanu","text_ar":"وَخَلَفَ اللَّبَنُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"or the like, of which this is a correct explanation: or the phrase thus explained in the TA, as from the A, may correctly mean"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He became altered for the worse, and corrupt;"},{"kind":"text","text":"agreeably with other explanations of the verb below.]) ―         -b8-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xalafa","text_ar":"خَلَفَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", also signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a man)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"retired, withdrew,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"went away"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"apart."},{"kind":"text","text":"(JK.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xalafato nafosahu Eani AlT~aEaAmi","text_ar":"خَلَفَتْ نَفْسَهُ عَنِ الطَّعَامِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xuluwfN","text_ar":"خُلُوفٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"His soul turned away from, avoided,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"shunned, the food, in consequence of disease."},{"kind":"text","text":"(JK, TA.) ―         -b9-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He fled."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Ham p. 411.) ―         -b10-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a man, Sgh)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ascended a mountain."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Sgh, K.)       -A2-  See also 2, first sentence.       -A3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xalafa","text_ar":"خَلَفَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Msb, K, &c.,) aor."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xuluwfN","text_ar":"خُلُوفٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Lh, Msb, TA, and Ham p. 679,) [inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xuluwfN","text_ar":"خُلُوفٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":",] said of the taste of water,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, different from,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"contrary to, what it was thought to be:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and [hence,]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, altered"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"for the worse"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (Ham ubi suprà:) [and] said of milk, (S, K,) and of food, (Lh, S, Msb, K,) and the like, (Lh, TA,) and some say"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xalufa","text_ar":"خَلُفَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xuluwfN","text_ar":"خُلُوفٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Lh, TA,) of both verbs, (TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, altered"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"for the worse"},{"kind":"text","text":"] (Lh, S, Msb, K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in taste,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in odour;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb, K;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Axlf","text_ar":"اخلف","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": or, said of milk,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the first signifies it became bad from being long kept;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or, as in the A, (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"what was good thereof became mixed"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xulifa","text_ar":"خُلِفَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", i. e."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xuliTa","text_ar":"خُلِطَ"},{"kind":"text","text":",)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with other milk:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Axlf","text_ar":"اخلف","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", said of milk, signifies also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, sour:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) and the first, said of [the beverage called]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nabiy*","text_ar":"نَبِيذ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it became bad."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.) Also, inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xuluwfN","text_ar":"خُلُوفٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Mgh, Msb, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xuluwfapN","text_ar":"خُلُوفَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xilofapN","text_ar":"خِلْفَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (L, TA,) said of the mouth (S, Mgh, Msb, K) of a person fasting, (S, Msb, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, altered"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"for the worse"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in odour;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Mgh, Msb, K;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Axlf","text_ar":"اخلف","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S, Msb, K.) It is said in a trad. that the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xuluwf","text_ar":"خُلُوف"},{"kind":"text","text":"of the mouth of one who is fasting is sweeter in the estimation of God than the odour of musk: or, accord. to some of the lawyers and of the relaters of traditions,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaluwf","text_ar":"خَلُوف"},{"kind":"text","text":"; but [SM says,] I think this to be a mistake, as several affirm it to be, while others say that it is of a bad dial. : accord. to one reading, it is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xilofap","text_ar":"خِلْفَة"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) ―         -b2-  [Hence,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xalafa","text_ar":"خَلَفَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eano xuluqi A^abiyhi","text_ar":"عَنْ خُلُقِ اَبِيهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xuluwfN","text_ar":"خُلُوفٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,) (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, altered"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"for the worse"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"from the natural disposition of his father."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA.) ―         -b3-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xalafa","text_ar":"خَلَفَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (ISk, S, K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xalofN","text_ar":"خَلْفٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xuluwfN","text_ar":"خُلُوفٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xalofa","text_ar":"خَلْفَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xalaAfapN","text_ar":"خَلَافَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xuluwfN","text_ar":"خُلُوفٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (TA;) (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a man)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, bad,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"corrupt."},{"kind":"text","text":"(ISk, S, K, TA.) ―         -b4-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xalafa","text_ar":"خَلَفَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xalaAfapN","text_ar":"خَلَافَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(IAth, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xuluwfN","text_ar":"خُلُوفٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a man)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, stupid,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"foolish;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"one who had little,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"no, intellect"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"understanding:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, * TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"unprofitable:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a frequent promise-breaker:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(IAth:) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xalafa","text_ar":"خَلَفَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Axlf","text_ar":"اخلف","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", said of a slave,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, idiotic, deficient in intellect,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"bereft of his intellect."},{"kind":"text","text":"(JK.)       -A4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xalafa","text_ar":"خَلَفَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xalofN","text_ar":"خَلْفٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, * K, * TA;) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Axlf","text_ar":"اخلف","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Astxlf","text_ar":"استخلف","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, K;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He drew water,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K, TA,)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"liA^aholihi","text_ar":"لِاَهْلِهِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"for his family:"},{"kind":"text","text":"[app. because he who does so leaves his family behind him: see 2, first sentence:] (K, TA:) [or] ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Astxlf","text_ar":"استخلف","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", said of a man, signifies"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AisotaEo*aba","text_ar":"اِسْتَعْذَبَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlmaA='","text_ar":"المَا=ء"},{"kind":"text","text":"[app. as meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he sought,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"drew,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"brought, sweet water:"},{"kind":"text","text":"see art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"E*b","text_ar":"عذب"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: and, accord. to IAar, you say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alqawoma","text_ar":"القَوْمَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^axolafotu","text_ar":"اَخْلَفْتُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning properly"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I carried sweet water to the people,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"party, when they were in the"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"season,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"herbage, called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rabiyE","text_ar":"رَبِيع"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and without sweet water,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"when they were by salt water:"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_ixolaAfN","text_ar":"اـِخْلَافٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[as meaning the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"carrying,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"drawing, of water"},{"kind":"text","text":",] being [properly] only in the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rbyE","text_ar":"ربيع"},{"kind":"text","text":": in other cases, metaphorically applied. (TA.) El-Hoteíäh says,"},{"kind":"quote","text":"↓ \n      lizugobK kaA^awolaAdi AlqaTaA raAva xalofuhaA\n                      \n                     \n                        EalaY EaAjizaAti Aln~ahoDi HumorK HawaASiluho"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:) ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"To,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"for, downy ones, like the young ones of the katà, whose procurer of water has been slow in coming to those lacking the power of spreading their wings for flight, red in their crops"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: he means ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mixolifuhaA","text_ar":"مِخْلِفُهَا","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaAlifuhaA","text_ar":"خَالِفُهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"], and has put in the place of this the inf. n.: and by"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HwASlh","text_ar":"حواصله"},{"kind":"text","text":", accord. to Ks, he means"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HawaASilu maA *akoronaA","text_ar":"حَوَاصِلُ مَا ذَكْرْنَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the crops of what we have mentioned"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: but Fr says that the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"h","text_ar":"ه"},{"kind":"text","text":"relates to the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zgb","text_ar":"زغب"},{"kind":"text","text":", exclusively of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EAjzAt","text_ar":"عاجزات"},{"kind":"text","text":", which [latter] has the sign of the pl. ; for every pl. that has the form of a sing. may be imagined to be a sing., as in the saying of the poet,"},{"kind":"quote","text":"mivolu AlfiraAxi nutifato HawaASiluho"},{"kind":"text","text":"[meaning “ like the young birds of which the crops have been plucked ”]; for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlfrAx","text_ar":"الفراخ"},{"kind":"text","text":"has not the sign of the pl., but has the form of a sing., like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlkitaAb","text_ar":"الكِتَاب"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlHijaAb","text_ar":"الحِجَاب"},{"kind":"text","text":": another says, [but this is very far-fetched,] that the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"h","text_ar":"ه"},{"kind":"text","text":"relates to"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlnhD","text_ar":"النهض"},{"kind":"text","text":", which [sometimes] means a place in the shoulderblade of the camel; and that the poet has used it metaphorically as belonging to the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qTA","text_ar":"قطا"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S.)       -A5-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xalafa Alv~awoba","text_ar":"خَلَفَ الثَّوْبَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlqamiySa","text_ar":"القَمِيصَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb, K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xalofN","text_ar":"خَلْفٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Kr, TA) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xulofapN","text_ar":"خُلْفَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in some copies of the K"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xalofapN","text_ar":"خَلْفَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", [so in my MS. copy of the K, and so in the TK,] and [in some]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xulafN","text_ar":"خُلَفٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"also, but these require consideration, (TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He took out from the garment,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"shirt, the part that was worn out,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb, K,) that is,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the middle part, which was worn out,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and then sewed the"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"cut"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"edges together."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb, K.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alv~awoba","text_ar":"الثَّوْبَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Axlf","text_ar":"اخلف","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies the same as"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xalafahu","text_ar":"خَلَفَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He repaired the garment"},{"kind":"text","text":"[app. in any manner, or, as is implied in the S and TA,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"by substituting one piece for another"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (S, K, TA.) ―         -b2-  The saying, in a trad. of Hamneh,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faA_i*aA xalafato *`lika falotagotasilo","text_ar":"فَاـِذَا خَلَفَتْ ذٰلِكَ فَلْتَغْتَسِلْ"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"And when she has discriminated that"},{"kind":"text","text":"period of days and nights during which she has been"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaAy^iD","text_ar":"حَايِض"},{"kind":"text","text":", ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"she shall perform a complete ablution of herself,"},{"kind":"text","text":"] is from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xalafa AlqamiyS","text_ar":"خَلَفَ القَمِيص"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifying as explained above. (Msb.)       -A6-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xalafa","text_ar":"خَلَفَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He mixed"},{"kind":"text","text":"[a thing with another thing; as, for instance, (see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xulifa","text_ar":"خُلِفَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"in a passage above,) milk with other milk]: and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he mixed"},{"kind":"text","text":"saffron, and medicine,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with water."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)       -A7-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xalafa bayotahu","text_ar":"خَلَفَ بَيْتَهُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He put to,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"made for, his tent, a pole,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA,) termed a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaAlifap","text_ar":"خَالِفَة"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the hinder part thereof."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K TA.)       -A8-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xalifa","text_ar":"خَلِفَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xalafN","text_ar":"خَلَفٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a camel)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"inclined towards one side."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xalafN","text_ar":"خَلَفٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is also an inf. n. (of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xalifa","text_ar":"خَلِفَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", said of a man, TK) signifying The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"being"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^axolaf","text_ar":"اَخْلَف"},{"kind":"text","text":"as meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"contrarious, hard in disposition, as though going with a leaning towards one side:"},{"kind":"text","text":"―         -b3-  and the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"being left-handed:"},{"kind":"text","text":"―         -b4-  and the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"being"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aHowal","text_ar":"اَحْوَل"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"squint-eyed"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (K.)       -A9-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xalifato","text_ar":"خَلِفَتْ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb, K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xalafN","text_ar":"خَلَفٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"She"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a camel)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, pregnant."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb, K.)"}],"source_refs":["TA","Mgh","K","S","Msb","Sgh","MF","AZ","L","JK","Lh","ISk","IAth","Kr"]}]}}